-- 12-recursive-requirement-extractor-frames.cell вҖ” full execution trace (R17, v0.2)
--
-- Ready set analysis (initial):
--   request: given text вүЎ "Build me a chat app" вҶ’ READY (literal binding)
--   extract-explicit: given requestвҶ’text вҶ’ BLOCKED (needs request)
--   extract-implicit: given requestвҶ’text, extract-explicitвҶ’requirements вҶ’ BLOCKED
--   assess-concreteness: given extract-explicitвҶ’requirements, extract-implicitвҶ’requirements вҶ’ BLOCKED
--   spawn-decomposers: given assess-concretenessвҶ’vague вҶ’ BLOCKED
--   decompose-template: given requirement вҶ’ BLOCKED (template, not directly invoked)
--   collect-requirements: given assess-concretenessвҶ’concrete, decomposer-*вҶ’... вҶ’ BLOCKED
--   refine-vague: given collect-requirementsвҶ’remaining-vague where length > 0 вҶ’ BLOCKED
--   format-spec: given collect-requirementsвҶ’all-requirements, requestвҶ’text вҶ’ BLOCKED
--   вҠўвҲҳ evolve: coordinates iteration over {extract-implicit, ..., refine-vague}
--
-- Ready set: { request }
--
-- v0.2 execution notes:
--   - вҠЁ? at file scope applies as default recovery for all cells
--   - Oracles on extract-implicit are aspirational under вҠўвҲҳ management
--   - Wildcard deps decomposer-*вҶ’field are v0.2-compliant
--   - вҠўвҠў spawn-decomposers uses accumulate mode (v0.2 default)
--   - Guard clause on refine-vague: skips when remaining-vague is empty
--   - Guard-induced вҠҘ: if refine-vague skips, its yields are вҠҘ (no downstream depends)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 0: request (soft cell, literal binding)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў request
  given text вүЎ "Build me a chat app"
  yield text

  вҲҙ (no вҲҙ body вҖ” text is directly bound via вүЎ)

  yield text вүЎ "Build me a chat app"

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ text is a vague software request with unstated assumptions вҶ’ вң“
--     "Build me a chat app" вҖ” no specifics about platform, scale, features,
--     users, storage, security, or deployment. Semantically vague.

-- Ready set after: { extract-explicit }
-- (requestвҶ’text now bound, satisfying extract-explicit's given)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 1: extract-explicit (soft cell, LLM evaluation)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў extract-explicit
  given requestвҶ’text вүЎ "Build me a chat app"
  yield requirements[]

  вҲҙ Read В«requestвҶ’textВ» and extract every explicitly stated requirement.
    An explicit requirement is something the request directly says or
    unambiguously implies from the literal words. For "Build me a chat app":
    - "chat" = messaging between parties
    - "app" = software application
    - "build" = create from scratch (not configure existing)
    - "me" = for the requester's use/ownership

    List each as a concrete, testable statement.

-- LLM evaluation:
-- The prompt asks for explicit requirements from the literal words.
-- "Build me a chat app" has four semantic tokens to unpack.

  yield requirements вүЎ [
    "The system must support sending and receiving text messages between two or more parties (from 'chat')",
    "The deliverable is a software application with a user interface (from 'app')",
    "The application must be built from scratch, not configured from an existing platform (from 'build')",
    "The application is for the requester's use or ownership (from 'me')"
  ]

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ each requirement is directly traceable to words in the request вҶ’ вң“
--     Each requirement cites its source word in parentheses.
--   вҠЁ each requirement is a testable statement (can verify pass/fail) вҶ’ вң“
--     "supports sending and receiving" вҖ” testable via message exchange test.
--     "software application with UI" вҖ” testable via existence check.
--     "built from scratch" вҖ” testable via provenance audit.
--     "for the requester" вҖ” testable via access/ownership check.
--   вҠЁ length(requirements) вүҘ 1 вҶ’ вң“ (4 requirements)

-- Ready set after: { extract-implicit }
-- (requestвҶ’text and extract-explicitвҶ’requirements both now bound)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- вҠўвҲҳ ITERATION 0 вҖ” initial extraction
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 2: extract-implicit v0 (soft cell, LLM evaluation, вҠўвҲҳ-managed)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў extract-implicit
  given requestвҶ’text вүЎ "Build me a chat app"
  given extract-explicitвҶ’requirements вүЎ [
    "The system must support sending and receiving text messages between two or more parties",
    "The deliverable is a software application with a user interface",
    "The application must be built from scratch",
    "The application is for the requester's use or ownership"
  ]
  yield requirements[], confidence[]

  вҲҙ Identify requirements NOT stated in В«requestвҶ’textВ» but implied by
    convention, domain knowledge, or reasonable user expectations.
    ...
    Do NOT include requirements already in В«extract-explicitвҶ’requirementsВ».

-- LLM evaluation:
-- The LLM draws on domain knowledge of chat applications to identify
-- unstated expectations. A "chat app" implies at minimum: user identity,
-- persistence, real-time delivery, and basic security.

  yield requirements вүЎ [
    "Users must be able to create accounts or authenticate to identify themselves",
    "Messages must be persisted so users can view conversation history",
    "Messages should be delivered in real-time (sub-second latency perceived by user)",
    "Message content must be private between conversation participants",
    "The app must support at least 1-on-1 conversations",
    "Users must receive notifications for new messages when not actively viewing the conversation",
    "The app should handle network disconnection gracefully and sync on reconnection"
  ]
  yield confidence вүЎ [
    "certain",
    "certain",
    "certain",
    "likely",
    "certain",
    "likely",
    "likely"
  ]

-- v0.2: oracle checks on вҠўвҲҳ-managed cells are aspirational (feedback signals):
--   вҠЁ no requirement in implicit duplicates one in extract-explicit вҶ’ вң“
--     Cross-checked: none of the 7 implicit requirements repeat the 4 explicit ones.
--   вҠЁ length(requirements) вүҘ 3 вҶ’ вң“ (7 requirements)
--   вҠЁ each requirement has a corresponding confidence level вҶ’ вң“ (7 requirements, 7 confidences)
--   вҠЁ each confidence вҲҲ {certain, likely, possible} вҶ’ вң“ (all values in set)
--
-- Under v0.2 вҠўвҲҳ semantics: these oracles are aspirational. All pass in this case,
-- but even if they failed, the cell would freeze and вҠўвҲҳ would drive improvement.

-- Ready set after: { assess-concreteness }
-- (extract-explicitвҶ’requirements and extract-implicitвҶ’requirements both bound)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 3: assess-concreteness (soft cell, LLM evaluation)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў assess-concreteness
  given extract-explicitвҶ’requirements вүЎ [
    "The system must support sending and receiving text messages between two or more parties",
    "The deliverable is a software application with a user interface",
    "The application must be built from scratch",
    "The application is for the requester's use or ownership"
  ]
  given extract-implicitвҶ’requirements вүЎ [
    "Users must be able to create accounts or authenticate to identify themselves",
    "Messages must be persisted so users can view conversation history",
    "Messages should be delivered in real-time (sub-second latency perceived by user)",
    "Message content must be private between conversation participants",
    "The app must support at least 1-on-1 conversations",
    "Users must receive notifications for new messages when not actively viewing the conversation",
    "The app should handle network disconnection gracefully and sync on reconnection"
  ]
  yield concrete[], vague[], concreteness-score

  вҲҙ For each requirement from both explicit and implicit lists, judge:
    Is this requirement concrete and testable as stated?
    ...

-- LLM evaluation:
-- The LLM evaluates each of the 11 requirements (4 explicit + 7 implicit)
-- for concreteness. Several are directionally correct but lack measurable
-- criteria вҖ” "real-time" means what latency? "Gracefully" means what behavior?

  yield concrete вүЎ [
    "The system must support sending and receiving text messages between two or more parties",
    "The deliverable is a software application with a user interface",
    "The application must be built from scratch",
    "The application is for the requester's use or ownership",
    "Users must be able to create accounts or authenticate to identify themselves",
    "The app must support at least 1-on-1 conversations"
  ]
  yield vague вүЎ [
    "Messages must be persisted so users can view conversation history вҖ” VAGUE: how far back? All history forever? What storage guarantees?",
    "Messages should be delivered in real-time вҖ” VAGUE: 'sub-second' is imprecise. What percentile? Under what load? What network conditions?",
    "Message content must be private between conversation participants вҖ” VAGUE: private how? End-to-end encryption? At-rest encryption? Access control only?",
    "Users must receive notifications for new messages вҖ” VAGUE: what channels? Push, email, in-app? What latency for notifications?",
    "The app should handle network disconnection gracefully and sync on reconnection вҖ” VAGUE: 'gracefully' is undefined. Queue messages? Show offline indicator? How long before timeout?"
  ]
  yield concreteness-score вүЎ 5.5

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ length(concrete) + length(vague) = length(explicit) + length(implicit) вҶ’ вң“
--     6 + 5 = 4 + 7 = 11
--   вҠЁ concreteness-score = 10 Г— 6 / (6 + 5) вҶ’ вң“
--     10 Г— 6 / 11 = 5.45 вүҲ 5.5 (rounded to one decimal)
--   вҠЁ each vague requirement explains why it's vague вҶ’ вң“
--     Each vague entry includes "VAGUE: ..." explanation.

-- Ready set after: { spawn-decomposers }
-- (assess-concretenessвҶ’vague now bound, В§decompose-template is static)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 4: spawn-decomposers (вҠўвҠў spawner, creates 5 decomposer cells)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠўвҠў spawn-decomposers
  given assess-concretenessвҶ’vague вүЎ [5 vague requirements]
  given В§decompose-template
  yield В§decomposer-cells[]
  until length(decomposer-cells) = length(assess-concretenessвҶ’vague)
  max 10
  accumulate

  вҲҙ For each vague requirement in В«assess-concretenessвҶ’vagueВ», spawn
    a decomposer cell that breaks it into concrete sub-requirements.
    ...

-- Spawner fires: creates 5 cells from В§decompose-template:
--   decomposer-0: requirement вүЎ "Messages must be persisted... VAGUE: how far back?"
--   decomposer-1: requirement вүЎ "Messages should be delivered in real-time... VAGUE: sub-second imprecise"
--   decomposer-2: requirement вүЎ "Message content must be private... VAGUE: private how?"
--   decomposer-3: requirement вүЎ "Users must receive notifications... VAGUE: what channels?"
--   decomposer-4: requirement вүЎ "The app should handle network disconnection... VAGUE: gracefully undefined"

  yield В§decomposer-cells вүЎ [decomposer-0, decomposer-1, decomposer-2, decomposer-3, decomposer-4]

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ length(decomposer-cells) = length(assess-concretenessвҶ’vague) вҶ’ вң“ (5 = 5)

-- Ready set after: { decomposer-0, decomposer-1, decomposer-2, decomposer-3, decomposer-4 }
-- (all 5 spawned cells have their requirement binding satisfied)
-- Under confluence, any order is valid. We evaluate them sequentially for clarity.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 5: decomposer-0 (spawned soft cell вҖ” message persistence)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў decomposer-0
  given requirement вүЎ "Messages must be persisted so users can view conversation history вҖ” VAGUE: how far back? All history forever? What storage guarantees?"
  yield sub-requirements[], all-concrete

  вҲҙ The requirement В«requirementВ» is vague. Break it into specific,
    testable sub-requirements. Each sub-requirement should be concrete
    enough to verify pass/fail in a test. If a sub-requirement is still
    vague, mark all-concrete as false вҖ” the вҠўвҲҳ loop will recurse.

-- LLM evaluation:
-- "Message persistence" decomposes into retention period, storage guarantees,
-- and retrieval capabilities.

  yield sub-requirements вүЎ [
    "All messages must be stored for a minimum of 365 days from creation",
    "Users can retrieve any message within the retention period in under 2 seconds",
    "Messages survive server restarts without data loss (durability guarantee)",
    "Conversation history is paginated with at least 50 messages per page load"
  ]
  yield all-concrete вүЎ true

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ each sub-requirement is more specific than the original вҶ’ вң“
--     Original: "persisted... how far back?" вҶ’ now: "365 days", "under 2 seconds", etc.
--   вҠЁ sub-requirements collectively cover the intent вҶ’ вң“
--     Retention + retrieval + durability + pagination covers persistence.
--   вҠЁ all-concrete вҲҲ {true, false} вҶ’ вң“
--   вҠЁ if all-concrete = true then every sub-requirement has a measurable criterion вҶ’ вң“
--     "365 days", "under 2 seconds", "survive restarts", "50 messages per page"

-- Ready set after: { decomposer-1, decomposer-2, decomposer-3, decomposer-4 }

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 6: decomposer-1 (spawned soft cell вҖ” real-time delivery)
