    -- From decomposer-1 (real-time, 4):
    "Delivery latency p50 < 200ms broadband",
    "Delivery latency p99 < 1000ms broadband",
    "Delivery latency p50 < 500ms mobile 4G",
    "Sustain latency targets under 10,000 concurrent users",
    -- From decomposer-2 (privacy, 3 concrete):
    "Only conversation participants can read messages (access control)",
    "Messages encrypted in transit via TLS 1.2+",
    "Messages encrypted at rest via AES-256",
    -- From decomposer-3 (notifications, 4):
    "In-app notifications within 1 second",
    "Push notifications within 5 seconds",
    "Users can disable push per conversation",
    "Notification preview shows first 100 characters",
    -- From decomposer-4 (network resilience, 5):
