--   decomposer-2        вҶ’ sub-requirements вүЎ [4], all-concrete вүЎ false
--   decomposer-3        вҶ’ sub-requirements вүЎ [4], all-concrete вүЎ true
--   decomposer-4        вҶ’ sub-requirements вүЎ [5], all-concrete вүЎ true
--   collect-requirements вҶ’ all-requirements вүЎ [26], remaining-vague вүЎ [1], completeness-score вүЎ 9.6
--   format-spec         вҶ’ specification вүЎ (structured document)
