-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- EXECUTION SUMMARY
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
--
-- Total eval-one steps: 12 (frames 0-11)
-- вҠўвҲҳ iterations: 1 (iteration 0 only) out of max 3
-- вҠўвҠў spawner firings: 1 (spawned 5 decomposer cells)
-- Convergence: completeness-score reached 9.6 on first iteration (threshold вүҘ 9)
--
-- Requirement extraction across pipeline:
--   Input:    1 vague request ("Build me a chat app")
--   Explicit: 4 requirements (directly traceable to words)
--   Implicit: 7 requirements (domain knowledge, confidence-rated)
--   Concrete: 6 of 11 passed concreteness assessment (score 5.5)
--   Vague:    5 of 11 sent to decomposer cells
--   After decomposition: 26 concrete + 1 remaining vague (score 9.6)
--   Final:    26 requirements in structured specification
--
-- Wildcard resolution:
--   decomposer-*вҶ’sub-requirements matched: decomposer-0 through decomposer-4
--   decomposer-*вҶ’all-concrete matched: same 5 cells
--   Resolved after all 5 spawned cells froze (frames 5-9)
