-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- OBSERVATIONS (v0.2-aware)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-spawner-wildcard-synergy
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "вҠўвҠў + WILDCARD DEPS ARE THE RECURSIVE DECOMPOSITION PATTERN: spawn-decomposers creates N cells dynamically, collect-requirements gathers their outputs via decomposer-*вҶ’sub-requirements. This is the v0.2 pattern at its best вҖ” spawners create, wildcards collect. Neither alone is sufficient. The spawner decides HOW MANY cells to create (driven by data). The wildcard waits for ALL of them (driven by the graph). Zero coordination code. The pattern appeared in R16 as ad-hoc notation; v0.2 makes it a first-class feature."

вҠў= obs-single-iteration-convergence
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "вҠўвҲҳ CONVERGED IN 1 ITERATION (of max 3): completeness-score hit 9.6 on the first pass. This is because the decomposer cells were highly effective вҖ” 4 of 5 produced fully concrete sub-requirements. Only decomposer-2 (privacy) marked all-concrete = false, and even it produced 3 of 4 concrete sub-requirements. The вҠўвҲҳ loop's max 3 iterations provided insurance that was not needed. The program's real work happens in the вҠўвҠў spawner expansion, not the вҠўвҲҳ iteration вҖ” the recursive decomposition strategy is more powerful than iterative refinement for this task."

вҠў= obs-guard-clause-not-needed
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "GUARD CLAUSE ON refine-vague WAS TRUE BUT CELL NEVER FIRED: the v0.2 guard (where length(remaining-vague) > 0) evaluated to TRUE (1 vague requirement remained), so the cell would have entered the ready set. But вҠўвҲҳ terminated before reaching refine-vague in the through chain. This shows the interaction between guard clauses and вҠўвҲҳ: guards gate the ready set, but вҠўвҲҳ termination gates the entire loop. In a hypothetical iteration where completeness < 9 and remaining-vague was empty, the guard would have correctly SKIPPED refine-vague, producing вҠҘ вҖ” preventing useless LLM calls on an empty list."

вҠў= obs-aspirational-oracles-all-passed
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 ASPIRATIONAL SEMANTICS WERE NOT TESTED: extract-implicit's oracles all passed on iteration 0, so we never observed the aspirational behavior (freeze despite oracle failure). This is the happy path вҖ” the semantics matter for the SAD path. A harder request (ambiguous domain, conflicting conventions) would likely trigger oracle failures in early iterations, and the aspirational semantics would prevent conflict between вҠЁ? retry and вҠўвҲҳ iteration. The v0.2 clarification remains necessary even when not exercised."

вҠў= obs-accumulate-mode-default
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "вҠўвҠў ACCUMULATE MODE IS CORRECT FOR THIS PATTERN: spawn-decomposers fired once and created 5 cells. If вҠўвҲҳ iterated again, the spawner would fire again with new vague requirements from the refined assessment, and NEW decomposer cells (decomposer-5, decomposer-6, ...) would accumulate alongside the originals. This is the right behavior вҖ” previous decompositions should not be discarded. The v0.2 explicit accumulate mode (default) matches the program's intent. Replace mode would be wrong here вҖ” it would destroy already-computed sub-requirements."

вҠў= obs-four-to-twenty-six-amplification
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "AMPLIFICATION RATIO 1:26 вҖ” from 5 words to 26 concrete requirements: 'Build me a chat app' (5 words) вҶ’ 4 explicit + 7 implicit вҶ’ 5 vague decomposed into 21 sub-requirements вҶ’ 26 total concrete requirements in a structured specification. This is Cell's value proposition for requirement extraction: the LLM applies domain knowledge (what chat apps need), the oracles enforce quality (testable, non-duplicate, confidence-rated), and the spawner provides recursive depth (vague вҶ’ concrete). A single LLM call would miss the recursion; a pipeline without oracles would miss the quality gates."

вҠў= obs-wildcard-resolution-timing
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "WILDCARD RESOLUTION TIMING VALIDATES v0.2 SEMANTICS: collect-requirements declares given decomposer-*вҶ’sub-requirements. This wildcard resolved against {decomposer-0, ..., decomposer-4} вҖ” all cells that matched the pattern at the time of ready-set computation. The cell became ready only after ALL 5 matching cells had frozen their sub-requirements field. If the spawner had created cells incrementally (e.g., async spawning), collect-requirements would have waited. The v0.2 spec's rule вҖ” 'wildcard re-resolves at each ready-set computation' вҖ” ensures correctness even under dynamic spawning."

вҠў= obs-file-scope-recovery-not-triggered
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 FILE-SCOPE вҠЁ? WORKED AS SAFETY NET: the file-scope вҠЁ? (retry max 3, then partial-accept(best)) was never triggered вҖ” all oracle checks passed on first evaluation. But it provides the safety net for a harder request where, say, extract-implicit fails to avoid duplicating explicit requirements, or decomposer cells fail to produce more-specific sub-requirements. The file-scope default means every cell in this program has recovery without per-cell вҠЁ? declarations вҖ” exactly the v0.2 design intent for reducing boilerplate."
